Title: S6 EP. 269 Lauren Prager - Make Every Day A Great Day
Description:
Hashtags: #iHeartRadio #ApplePodcasts #GooglePlay #Spotify #Stitcher #Podbean #YouTube #Employers4Change #E4C #internships #radio #podcast #innovation #employers #smallbusiness #business #FutureOfWork #ValenciaCollegeRadio 
 
This week’s guest did not disappoint and you will want to reach out to her right away and learn more about Synapse and how you can get involved. When I first met Lauren Prager at a Synapse Florida event, I was impressed with her positivity, it was infectious in all the right ways. As I got to know her better I learned more about the organization and how well connected she is to so many resources that everyone in innovation or technology will want to tap into.  I have several favorite parts that I believe my listeners will find valuable to hear. Lauren’s mentoring advice is the first nugget, the second is her mantra that she lives her life by, and the third is how we should engage with ethical use of AI.  I hope you enjoy the show; please leave us a comment, share the episode and tag a friend to help us grow our fanbase.
